Required parameters

  • public_id

    A textual identifier that uniquely identifies a locality, returned from an Address Autocomplete.

Optional parameters

  • cc_format

    To specify the format for the short country code expected to be returned in the address_components field (default is alpha3).

  • fields

    Used to limit the returning fields (by default, all fields are return). Available fields are (geometry) (fields should be separated by a ,). By using this parameter you will limit content of responses to the geometry part. No address component will be returned.
